race.comment: AEROPLANE PENNY (1) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 0.8 lengths (17.42). Form reads well for this. COMMON CHAOS (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (17.59) in a Free For All at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Expected to do much better this time. JUNK YARD HIPPY (3) scored (17.30) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Has definite claims. WILD MOOD (6) is another with top-three prospects.
